-- int_deduped_returns.sql
```sql
WITH source AS (
    SELECT
        item_id,
        return_date,
        reason,
        status,
        ROW_NUMBER() OVER (
            PARTITION BY item_id
            ORDER BY 
                CASE WHEN status = 'approved' THEN 0 ELSE 1 END,
                return_date ASC
        ) AS row_num
    FROM {{ ref('stg_returns') }}
)
SELECT
    item_id,
    return_date,
    reason,
    status
FROM source
WHERE row_num = 1
```

-- fct_product_return_rates.sql
```sql
WITH source AS (
    SELECT
        oi.item_id,
        oi.product_id,
        oi.quantity,
        oi.unit_price,
        COALESCE(p.name, '(unknown)') AS product_name,
        COALESCE(p.category_id, NULL) AS category_id,
        COALESCE(c.name, '(unknown)') AS category_name,
        COALESCE(r.return_date, NULL) AS return_date
    FROM {{ ref('stg_order_items') }} oi
    LEFT JOIN {{ ref('stg_products') }} p
        ON p.product_id = oi.product_id
    LEFT JOIN {{ ref('stg_categories') }} c
        ON c.category_id = p.category_id
    LEFT JOIN {{ ref('int_deduped_returns') }} r
        ON r.item_id = oi.item_id
    WHERE r.status = 'approved'
)
SELECT
    category_name,
    COUNT(*) AS total_items_sold,
    SUM(CASE WHEN return_date IS NOT NULL THEN quantity ELSE 0 END) AS total_items_returned,
    CASE 
        WHEN total_items_sold > 0 THEN ROUND(
            CAST(SUM(CASE WHEN return_date IS NOT NULL THEN quantity ELSE 0 END) AS DECIMAL(10,4)) / 
            CAST(total_items_sold AS DECIMAL(10,4)) * 100,
            2
        ) ELSE 0 
    END AS return_rate
FROM source
GROUP BY
    category_name
ORDER BY
    return_rate DESC
